Read a *_prot.txt file from IMGTHLA.

Usage

read_prot(prot_file)

Arguments

prot_file

File name for a txt file from IMGTHLA like "DQB1_prot.txt"

Value

A list with a dataframe and a matrix. The dataframe has two columns:

  • allele: the name of the allele, e.g., DQB*01:01

  • seq: the amino acid sequence The matrix has a one-hot encoding of the variants among the alleles, with one row for each allele and one column for each amino acid at each position.
